PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ROBERT D. GUIBORD of Cumberland, Ontario, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Norma J. Lamont, whose term has expired.
